2. Implement robust server-side password strength validation:
   - Enforce minimum 12-16 characters
   - Require uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, and special characters
   - Reject common/dictionary passwords using a comprehensive blacklist (password, admin, test, 123456, etc.)
   - Implement password strength meter library (e.g., zxcvbn for JavaScript)

